# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# military.ese — 兵法词库 / Military Strategy Vocabulary
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 孙子兵法 (Sun Tzu's Art of War) as strategy patterns.
# Military operations map to system operations:
#
#   攻 (Gōng)  — Attack       → SEND request / push data
#   守 (Shǒu)  — Defend       → RECEIVE / buffer / protect
#   退 (Tuì)   — Withdraw     → BACKOFF / retry with delay
#   进 (Jìn)   — Advance      → PROCEED / next phase
#   伏 (Fú)    — Ambush       → LAZY_EVAL / on-demand compute
#   围 (Wéi)   — Surround     → CIRCLE / round-robin
#   分 (Fēn)   — Divide       → SPLIT / partition
#   合 (Hé)    — Unite        → MERGE / aggregate
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Domain declaration ──────────────────────────────────────
@domain: 兵 (military)
@description: 孙子兵法词库 — 军事策略映射为系统操作

# ── Core operations ─────────────────────────────────────────
攻 → ATTACK       # Attack: send request, push forward
守 → DEFEND       # Defend: buffer, protect, receive
退 → WITHDRAW     # Withdraw: backoff, retry later
进 → ADVANCE      # Advance: proceed to next phase
伏 → AMBUSH       # Ambush: lazy evaluation, deferred compute
围 → SURROUND     # Surround: round-robin, wrap-around
分 → SPLIT        # Divide: partition, shard data
合 → MERGE        # Unite: aggregate, combine results

# ── Terrain → infrastructure ────────────────────────────────
山 → MOUNTAIN     # Mountain: high-latency path
水 → WATER        # Water: streaming data
林 → FOREST       # Forest: dense, complex topology
火 → FIRE         # Fire: emergency shutdown / purge

# ── Force composition ──────────────────────────────────────
正 → DIRECT       # Direct force: synchronous path
奇 → INDIRECT     # Indirect force: asynchronous path
虚 → VACANT       # Empty: available capacity
实 → FULL         # Full: at capacity

# ── Sun Tzu patterns ────────────────────────────────────────
# 知己知彼 → SELF_PROFILE + OPPONENT_PROFILE → DECIDE
# 兵者诡道也 → ALL_COMMUNICATION_IS_ENCRYPTED
# 不战而屈人之兵 → RESOLVE_WITHOUT_COMPUTE (cache hit)
# 出其不意 → SURPRISE_DISPATCH (async callback)
